WEBVTT

00:00:13.309 --> 00:00:17.538
haynt iz yul der eyn un draysikster, nayntsn nayntsik zibn.

00:00:17.646 --> 00:00:21.184
ibergelebter dem HOLOCAUST iz BERNAT LANDO

00:00:21.392 --> 00:00:23.664
un der TAPE iz numer tsvey.

00:00:25.240 --> 00:00:29.233
ir hot undz dertseylt az me hot bay aykh tsugenumen dem mil.

00:00:28.783 --> 00:00:29.587
yo.

00:00:29.442 --> 00:00:32.912
ve- ver hot, velkhe makht hot dos tsugenumen? di rumenishe?

00:00:32.800 --> 00:00:36.996
der, ⟨bay undz⟩ hot tsugenumen dem mil der e- ungarishe makht

00:00:37.170 --> 00:00:38.159
in

00:00:38.368 --> 00:00:40.336
eyn un fertsiker yor.

00:00:41.035 --> 00:00:43.493
di gantse hoyz iz geblibn

00:00:43.920 --> 00:00:46.766
on a parnose, nisht gehat fun vos tsu lebn.

00:00:47.835 --> 00:00:51.440
dos hoyz hot men ge- nokh gelozt mit di felder.

00:00:52.898 --> 00:00:54.725
dos ⟨iz⟩ ober veynik geven.

00:00:54.725 --> 00:00:55.844
iz geganen

00:00:55.935 --> 00:01:00.974
mayn sh- hob ikh gehat a shvester vos zi iz geven in di mil iz geven zeyer a geshikte

00:01:01.133 --> 00:01:03.742
zi iz ar- alts aropgeforn oyf Pest

00:01:04.525 --> 00:01:05.886
un zi hot gebrengt

00:01:07.444 --> 00:01:12.433
f- skhoyre. zi hot farkoyft far di poyerim dortn. in dem hot men fardint a bisl gelt

00:01:13.418 --> 00:01:14.357
vayl

00:01:14.667 --> 00:01:19.436
zi hot oykh nisht gekent alts geyn vayl mir ho'mir gehat a milner

00:01:19.695 --> 00:01:20.870
vos er hot

00:01:21.130 --> 00:01:23.267
tsugenumen di mil fun undz

00:01:23.374 --> 00:01:26.743
un er hot gelozt mayn shvester internirn.

00:01:26.867 --> 00:01:30.675
er hot ir gegebn, hot ⟨ir⟩ geshribn a tsetl az zi iz

00:01:31.322 --> 00:01:32.294
a

00:01:32.453 --> 00:01:35.096
⟨es tut zi partazirn⟩ mit di komunistn.

00:01:35.777 --> 00:01:39.399
mit dem hot men zi internirt. zi hot zikh gebroykht geyn meldn

00:01:39.405 --> 00:01:43.010
zibn kilometer ⟨yedn in der⟩ vokh tsu di

00:01:43.911 --> 00:01:46.284
tsu di politsey, tsu di zhandarn.

00:01:47.016 --> 00:01:51.296
un zi hot nor gekent forn fun montik biz donershtik.

00:01:51.538 --> 00:01:53.337
azoy hot men gelebt.

00:01:53.563 --> 00:01:54.367
un

00:01:54.492 --> 00:01:56.089
ikh bin arayn

00:01:56.314 --> 00:01:57.590
in der arbet

00:01:57.951 --> 00:01:59.244
arbets tsvang

00:01:59.588 --> 00:02:00.597
alts

00:02:00.597 --> 00:02:01.809
yunger man

00:02:02.085 --> 00:02:04.998
un di sh- familye hot zeyer shver gelebt.

00:02:06.287 --> 00:02:10.806
un m'hot, ikh bin geganen betn tsu dem milner eyn mol er zol mir gebn a bisl

00:02:10.806 --> 00:02:12.170
kukuruts mel

00:02:12.430 --> 00:02:15.849
me zol makhn nakht mol far di familye, hot er nisht gevolt gebn.

00:02:15.990 --> 00:02:17.570
er hot mikh nisht gevolt derkenen.

00:02:17.880 --> 00:02:19.933
lomer zikh kern a bisl tsurik.

00:02:20.293 --> 00:02:23.257
ven zaynen ongekumen tsu aykh di HUNGARN?

00:02:23.382 --> 00:02:24.121
in

00:02:24.121 --> 00:02:28.117
in nayn un draysik. in nayn un draysik ober fertsik.

00:02:28.933 --> 00:02:31.036
ikh gedenk nisht punk- dakht zikh mir in fertsik.

00:02:32.038 --> 00:02:36.942
beys zaynen gevezn di RUMANIEN, hot men ayer mil nit getrogn? nit tsugenumen bay aykh?

00:02:36.527 --> 00:02:38.276
neyn, di rumener nisht.

00:02:38.704 --> 00:02:43.760
az es zaynen gekumen di HUNGARN, iz gevezn a, vos iz gevezn, a bafel? iz gevezn a

00:02:44.222 --> 00:02:45.720
epes iz geve-

00:02:44.745 --> 00:02:47.489
a bafel fun oyvn, vayl se, me tut

00:02:47.732 --> 00:02:50.707
az di yidn hobn nisht keyn rekhts tsu hobn gornisht

00:02:50.707 --> 00:02:51.844
nisht keyn

00:02:52.727 --> 00:02:57.086
gesheftn, nisht keyn fabrikn, nisht gornisht. ales hot men tsugenumen

00:02:57.086 --> 00:02:59.404
un m'hot es ahingegebn far di

00:03:00.186 --> 00:03:01.563
far di kristn

00:03:01.637 --> 00:03:02.880
far di ungarn.

00:03:02.937 --> 00:03:06.306
hot men aykh batsolt far dem epes?

00:03:04.905 --> 00:03:06.525
absolut gornisht.

00:03:06.525 --> 00:03:08.139
keyn eyn groshn. nit a mol

00:03:08.139 --> 00:03:10.406
tsu esn hot men undz nisht gegebn. gornisht.

00:03:10.277 --> 00:03:13.275
zogt mir, der balebos ⟨vos⟩ iz gevorn fun der mil

00:03:13.281 --> 00:03:15.367
hot er getsolt far dem vos

00:03:15.205 --> 00:03:19.586
er hot nisht gornisht. ikh zog dokh az ven ikh bin gan tsun im betn far gelt

00:03:19.677 --> 00:03:23.485
a bisl mel hot er mir nisht gevolt gebn. far andere hot er farkoyft

00:03:23.507 --> 00:03:26.589
un fun mir vayl ikh bin geven a yid, hot er mir nisht gevolt gebn.

00:03:27.118 --> 00:03:29.508
dos heyst az bay aykh hot men tsugenumen

00:03:29.435 --> 00:03:30.305
un

00:03:29.515 --> 00:03:31.044
un avekgegebn

00:03:31.506 --> 00:03:33.390
avekgegebn far a goy

00:03:33.463 --> 00:03:36.072
un der goy hot mikh nisht gevolt derkenen mer.

00:03:36.248 --> 00:03:38.334
er iz geven mayn ayngeshtelter.

00:03:36.282 --> 00:03:37.322
ir hot geke-

00:03:38.965 --> 00:03:41.422
er iz geven der ayngeshtelter in der mil

00:03:43.217 --> 00:03:46.434
un er hot es gebetn fun di BEHORDE

00:03:46.592 --> 00:03:48.546
dos heyst, m'hot es

00:03:48.546 --> 00:03:51.682
azoy shriftlekh hot er es gebetn. m'hot dos im gegebn

00:03:52.093 --> 00:03:55.833
un er hot nisht gevolt derkenen, iz er geven dem, undzer ayngeshtelter.

00:03:55.924 --> 00:03:59.144
zogt mir, vi lang hot er gearbet mit ay- bay aykh?

00:03:59.144 --> 00:04:02.229
ot der ayngeshtelter vos iz gevezn far UNK

00:04:00.784 --> 00:04:02.308
der ayngeshtelter

00:04:02.308 --> 00:04:06.442
er hot geda- gearbet hipshe yorn. pinktlekh veys ikh nisht, ober

00:04:06.442 --> 00:04:08.304
fir finef yor hot er gearbet.

00:04:08.479 --> 00:04:10.953
vi zaynen geven ayere batsiungen mit im?

00:04:10.622 --> 00:04:15.167
zeyer gut. undz ho'mir alts zeyer gut geven. mir ho'mir nisht gevust az er iz aza groyser

00:04:15.167 --> 00:04:17.467
antisemit, aza groyser roshe.

00:04:17.625 --> 00:04:19.475
nor nokh dem hobn mir gezen,

00:04:19.583 --> 00:04:23.239
UNK ven, ven di ungern zenen arayngekumen, hot er gevizn ver er iz

00:04:24.325 --> 00:04:27.677
ober befor hobn mir nisht ⟨in akht⟩ genumen, vayl er iz geve- s'ho- s

00:04:27.750 --> 00:04:31.392
er hot moyre gehat, m'vet im aroysge- -varfn fun di postn

00:04:31.392 --> 00:04:33.245
hot er zikh tsugeshmeykhlt

00:04:33.522 --> 00:04:36.047
ober geven iz er, hot er undz gevolt

00:04:36.778 --> 00:04:37.970
tsu grunt leygn.

00:04:38.601 --> 00:04:44.012
m'hot bay aykh tsugenumen di mil. vos iz forgekumen mit di erd UNK velkher ir hot gearbet? mit di velder?

00:04:43.782 --> 00:04:46.225
di erd mit di velder

00:04:46.225 --> 00:04:48.715
hot men, azoy fil gehat, fun

00:04:48.715 --> 00:04:53.875
erd hot men gehat ⟨vos⟩ m'hot geboyt aleyn, gentslekh aleyn gezeyt un geboyt

00:04:53.923 --> 00:04:55.689
⟨vos⟩ m'hot nisht a sakh gekont.

00:04:55.864 --> 00:05:00.144
mir zenen geven kleyne kinder nokh, un der tate hot shoyn nisht getoygt, shoyn geven an elterer mentsh.

00:05:00.471 --> 00:05:02.231
deys iz geven fun der erd

00:05:02.231 --> 00:05:03.283
un

00:05:03.677 --> 00:05:08.492
un holts hot men geganen in vald, hot men gemegt brengen nor

00:05:08.492 --> 00:05:10.475
opgebrokhene, trukene

00:05:10.475 --> 00:05:13.951
shtiker holts. fun eygn vald hot men nisht gelozt brengen

00:05:13.951 --> 00:05:16.411
oyf, m'hot g- dos genumen tsu heytsn.

00:05:17.380 --> 00:05:19.652
un farkoyfn hot ir dos gekent?

00:05:18.747 --> 00:05:21.694
farkoyfn hobn mir nisht gehat gornisht mer.

00:05:21.784 --> 00:05:23.280
ales hot men tsugenumen.

00:05:23.455 --> 00:05:24.529
nisht gelozt.

00:05:24.822 --> 00:05:28.630
ir zogt az di erd hot men ibergelozn far aykh un di velder.

00:05:27.252 --> 00:05:34.074
di erd hot men ibergelozt, ober, di erd iz, iz, s'iz nisht geven gute felder dortn. s'iz geven shvakhe felder.

00:05:34.074 --> 00:05:37.589
m'hot gebroykht a sakh baarbetn, zol men epes produtsirn.

00:05:37.090 --> 00:05:39.261
hot ir dos nit gekent farkoyfn?

00:05:39.368 --> 00:05:40.324
neyn.

00:05:41.072 --> 00:05:45.200
vos farkoyfn? ver zol es koyfn? nishto dortn azelekhe men- zol es kenen opkoyfn.

00:05:45.949 --> 00:05:48.840
s'iz nisht geven halb aza gute felder

00:05:48.840 --> 00:05:50.162
me zol es zukhn.

00:05:50.674 --> 00:05:52.372
s'iz nisht geven keyn koynim deroyf.

00:05:53.138 --> 00:05:55.832
un mit vos hot ir zikh farnumen? vi hot ir gelebt?

00:05:55.990 --> 00:06:01.164
ayer mishpokhe? ir hot gezogt ayer shvester hot ge- a bisl ge- ge-

00:05:57.255 --> 00:05:58.565
ikh, dos, ikh ken

00:05:59.702 --> 00:06:03.482
yo, dos ikh denk ikh nokh ven m'iz geven in der heym, ober ikh bin dokh arayn in

00:06:03.482 --> 00:06:05.992
tsvangs arbet, veys ikh nisht pinktlekh

00:06:05.992 --> 00:06:09.520
tsu zogn vi azoy di familye gelebt, nor ikh shtel mir for

00:06:09.520 --> 00:06:11.174
s'iz zeyer shver geven

00:06:11.174 --> 00:06:13.567
vayl ikh hob bakumen eyn mol urloyb

00:06:14.147 --> 00:06:15.156
ende

00:06:15.156 --> 00:06:16.638
dray un fertsik

00:06:16.864 --> 00:06:18.950
onfang fir un fertsik

00:06:18.957 --> 00:06:22.005
hob ikh bakumen akht un tsvontsik tog urloyb

00:06:22.315 --> 00:06:23.946
bin ikh geven in der heym

00:06:24.188 --> 00:06:27.067
ober ikh hob mer geveynt ⟨a- vi⟩ gevoynt.

00:06:28.592 --> 00:06:30.504
kh'hob gezen di tsores vos iz

00:06:30.504 --> 00:06:32.451
un ikh hob gevust ikh broykh tsurikgeyn.

00:06:32.727 --> 00:06:35.488
kh'hob nisht gevolt tsurikgeyn. kh'hob gevolt avekloyfn

00:06:35.798 --> 00:06:37.187
un s'iz nisht

00:06:37.187 --> 00:06:38.306
gelungen

00:06:38.413 --> 00:06:43.317
un ikh bin tsurik arayn, un ikh bin lebn geblibn, un zey hob ikh mer keyn mol nisht gezen.

00:06:44.303 --> 00:06:50.962
zogt mir, az ir zay- vi s'iz forgekumen az m'hot aykh tsugenumen tsu der armey, tsu der tsving

00:06:51.070 --> 00:06:52.869
getsvungene arbetn.

00:06:53.010 --> 00:06:54.253
onfang

00:06:54.900 --> 00:07:00.069
ven ikh bin arayn oyf di Kashoyer vald vos ikh hob gearbet, dortn hob ikh gemakht a shtroz

00:07:00.069 --> 00:07:03.449
iz nisht azoy shlekht geven, vayl s'iz nisht geven keyn andere

00:07:03.675 --> 00:07:06.554
soldatn iber undz, nor undzer eygene.

00:07:06.932 --> 00:07:09.637
dey zenen geven z- z- zibetsn

00:07:09.637 --> 00:07:10.942
soldatn

00:07:11.067 --> 00:07:13.238
un tsvey ofitsirn

00:07:13.648 --> 00:07:16.041
dey zenen oykh geven nor rezerv

00:07:16.041 --> 00:07:18.924
nisht keyn stabile militer

00:07:19.217 --> 00:07:22.285
dey hobn zikh oykh nisht gekent ⟨azoy⟩ oyffirn vi azoy

00:07:22.285 --> 00:07:23.430
tsu shlekht.

00:07:23.672 --> 00:07:26.399
shpeter hot men undz avekgetrogn

00:07:27.182 --> 00:07:30.517
oyf an ander plats, un s'hot geheysn S-

00:07:30.709 --> 00:07:33.065
SZERETFALVA oyf ungerish

00:07:33.072 --> 00:07:35.563
oyf Rumenish heyst es SARATEL.

00:07:35.991 --> 00:07:40.895
dortn hobn mir, hot men getrogn, m'hot undz geboy- mir ho'mir geboyt ⟨shtitsyonen⟩

00:07:41.323 --> 00:07:43.075
farshidene pletser

00:07:43.075 --> 00:07:44.282
farshidene

00:07:44.282 --> 00:07:48.576
derfer vos iz geven, der tsug iz geganen, hot men geboyt naye

00:07:48.576 --> 00:07:51.681
⟨shtitsyonen⟩. dort hobn mir undz geboyt. dos ho'mir undz

00:07:51.681 --> 00:07:52.488
gemakht.

00:07:52.663 --> 00:07:55.255
fun dort hot men undz vayter avekgetrogn

00:07:55.330 --> 00:07:59.005
oyf MAROSHEVIZ. azoy heyst es oyf ungarish.

00:07:59.005 --> 00:08:02.169
oyf rumenish hey- ⟨rumeniish⟩ heyst es

00:08:02.169 --> 00:08:03.676
TOPLITA ROMANA.

00:08:04.172 --> 00:08:06.514
dortn ze'mir shoyn geven a lange tsayt.

00:08:06.514 --> 00:08:07.915
mir ho'mir gearbet

00:08:07.915 --> 00:08:10.910
di ban UNK, di ban zol kenen forn

00:08:10.910 --> 00:08:11.931
un kumen

00:08:11.931 --> 00:08:14.175
mir ho'mir farrokhtn. m'hot undz oysgelernt

00:08:14.175 --> 00:08:15.641
un dos hobn mir gearbet.

00:08:16.913 --> 00:08:21.663
ver zaynen gevezn di ⟨zeler⟩, arbeter vos zaynen gevezn tsuzamen mit aykh?

00:08:21.663 --> 00:08:24.463
vos far a natsyonale- ze- ⟨natsyonalitetn⟩?

00:08:23.477 --> 00:08:26.829
d- s'iz geven ungerishe VORARBEITERS

00:08:27.865 --> 00:08:32.029
iz zey hobn undz gevizn vos me broykht tsu makhn, vos nisht. m'hot, m'hot gemakht.

00:08:32.029 --> 00:08:33.987
m'hot ales gemakht vi se kert tsu zayn.

00:08:33.987 --> 00:08:37.126
onfang iz take shver geven. mir ho'mir nisht gevust vi azoy.

00:08:37.126 --> 00:08:39.615
zey hobn undz oysgelernt, iz geganen gring

00:08:39.615 --> 00:08:41.319
iz nisht shver geven di arbet.

00:08:41.319 --> 00:08:44.311
shpeter, fun dortn hot men undz avekgetrogn

00:08:44.672 --> 00:08:46.134
tsu di karpatn.

00:08:47.457 --> 00:08:49.003
lomir zikh opshteln a vayle.

00:08:49.144 --> 00:08:51.112
dertseylt u- az ir zayt gevezn

00:08:51.152 --> 00:08:58.672
ir hot dortn gearbet., ver zaynen geven di arbeter? vos far a natsyonali- natsyonalitet? farsheydene, oder nor yidn zaynen gevezn dort?

00:08:57.649 --> 00:08:58.667
nor yidn.

00:08:58.667 --> 00:09:01.946
nor undzere dos. undz aleyn ho'mir gearbet, nor der VOR-

00:09:01.159 --> 00:09:02.368
⟨reyne⟩ yidn.

00:09:02.104 --> 00:09:06.165
aro- reyne yidn, nor der VORMANN iz geven an ungarisher.

00:09:06.508 --> 00:09:08.729
ales hobn mir gehat, ⟨nor⟩ di yidn hobn gearbet.

00:09:08.230 --> 00:09:12.189
ver zaynen gevezn di ofitsern? di soldatn zaynen geven oykh yidishe?

00:09:12.077 --> 00:09:17.353
⟨nokh⟩ neyn, ⟨nokh⟩ nor kristn. nisht geven keyn yidisher soldat hot men ge- iz nisht geven.

00:09:17.005 --> 00:09:20.745
d- v- z- vos hobn d- di yidn zaynen gevezn nor arbeter?

00:09:19.553 --> 00:09:23.912
nor arbet. nor arbet in tsivile kleyder, nisht in keyn

00:09:23.912 --> 00:09:26.027
in, nisht keyn, in keyn uniform.

00:09:25.999 --> 00:09:30.735
zogt mir, ir zayt, beys ir hot gearbet, vu hot ir dortn gevoynt? vos hot ir zikh gegesn?

00:09:30.876 --> 00:09:33.013
vi iz ayer lebn forgekumen?

00:09:32.040 --> 00:09:35.830
mir ho'mir gevoynt in farshidene pletser in barakn.

00:09:35.830 --> 00:09:38.470
m'hot undz gegebn barakn tsu sh- voynen.

00:09:38.571 --> 00:09:41.299
m'hot undz gekokht. mir ho'mir gehat a kokh.

00:09:41.558 --> 00:09:43.070
m'hot undz gegebn

00:09:44.828 --> 00:09:48.690
finef un ferts- fir hundert un fuftsik gram broyt a tog

00:09:49.388 --> 00:09:51.879
un m'hot undz gekokht tsu esn.

00:09:52.290 --> 00:09:57.093
ver s'hot gegesn treyfes hot gegesn fun di kokh, un ver nisht

00:09:57.370 --> 00:10:02.561
hot zikh aleyn farkokht vi azoy er hot gekont. er hot hunger gelitn, vos er hot gekont. dos broyt hot er yo genutst.

00:10:03.478 --> 00:10:05.935
vu hot ir genumen gelt tsu koyfn

00:10:05.942 --> 00:10:07.168
tsu kokhn

00:10:06.128 --> 00:10:09.767
gelt hot men gehat. m'hot gekent koyfn. m'hot aroysgelozt

00:10:10.060 --> 00:10:15.842
es zol i- in dorf arayn, me zol koyfn vos m.'hot gebroykht, ober m'ho- s'iz nisht zeyer geven tsu bakumen vos tsu koyfn

00:10:16.590 --> 00:10:18.406
⟨ven⟩ s'iz shoyn geven ales

00:10:19.223 --> 00:10:22.941
m- mit kartn, mit ⟨tiketn⟩, vos m'hot gekoyft un vos nisht

00:10:22.941 --> 00:10:25.292
hot men nisht zeyer gekent a sakh zakhn koyfn.

00:10:27.019 --> 00:10:32.126
ir hot gelebt in barakn. zaynen zey gevezn varem? i- vintertsayt hot ir oykh gelebt in barakn?

00:10:32.065 --> 00:10:36.325
m- vinter hobn mir oykh gelebt ⟨in di⟩ barakn. mir hobn zikh genumen holts, un mir ho'mir geheytst

00:10:36.325 --> 00:10:38.615
m'hot nisht ge- zeyer gelozt, ober

00:10:38.680 --> 00:10:44.732
zey hobn nisht ge- zey hobn shtil geshvign. zey hobn nisht gezogt gornisht, vayl m'hot nisht gekent. s'iz geven groyse keltn. dortn iz geven zeyer kalt.

00:10:45.379 --> 00:10:49.811
un mir ho'mir geheytst. mir ho'mir geganvet holts fun vu mir hobn gekont

00:10:49.851 --> 00:10:54.873
un mir ho'mir gebrengt, un mir ho'mir geheytst. bay tog zenen mir dokh nisht geven in der heym, nor oyf di, bay nakht

00:10:55.285 --> 00:11:00.054
iz geven a sakh mol bay nakht, dos fayer hot zikh oysgeloshn. kh'hob mir ongegreyt vaser.

00:11:00.060 --> 00:11:04.391
